org.gag.node

Class UniqueID

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gag.node.UniqueID

  • public class UniqueID
extends java.lang.Object
    This class generates a random ID. This ID is used to identify a node for the GAG tree. Each ID is unique. An ID is composed by a head String "ID_" followed by an Integer number.
    Author:
    Andre GUENEY
